Text:
Do you have any of these Kismet Videos?

Weaken
Dr. Katja
Hypnotic Fun Vol. 3
Intoxicated
Look Into My Eyes
Programed

If so could you please upload them?

Thanks!

Yes, I have most of them. Unfortunately, for now, I have my hard disk a bit full to keep the ones I have uploaded and the ones you are requesting. As soon as I see that most of people are not downloading the current ones anymore and that there are seeders around, I will start replacing them and your list is a good start. So, keep an eye on my list and, please, keep seeding the ones you downloaded.  BTW, Look into my Eyes is on my current list and so, go for it asap.
Thanks N. Gull. U are the best. pls continue to upload!

I believe that credits must be given where credits are due and good work should be rewarded. So, if you really liked the content, consider supporting the producers and buy an original so they can continue to produce their stuff. Some have a very good quality and are quite affordable. It's a way to show our gratitude. Take it as a try before buy.
